  displayName:
    TranslatableName: Merlin Vaccum Engine
    plainText: 1
  description:
    TranslatableName: "This engine provides more \u2206V than the 1st stage thanks
      to it's impressive 165:1 nozzle expansion ratio. Has the option to have a shortened
      nozzle when 15% less thrust is needed for lighter payloads in order to save
      on valuble niobium metal. When shortened however,it is lighter. Foil is homemade
      lol..."
    plainText: 1
